<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>and we continue</title>
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="180x180" href="/favicon_io/apple-touch-icon.png">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="/favicon_io/favicon-32x32.png">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="16x16" href="/favicon_io/favicon-16x16.png">
    <link rel="manifest" href="/favicon_io/site.webmanifest">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/101668a678.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src= "https://player.twitch.tv/js/embed/v1.js"></script>
    <script src="/socket.io/socket.io.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/p5.js/1.1.9/p5.min.js" integrity="sha512-WIklPM6qPCIp6d3fSSr90j+1unQHUOoWDS4sdTiR8gxUTnyZ8S2Mr8e10sKKJ/bhJgpAa/qG068RDkg6fIlNFA==" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <!-- Main Module -->
    <script type="module" src="script.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">

        <!-- The streaming player -->
        <div id="stream-container"></div>

        <!-- The sketch! -->
        <div id="sketch-container">
            <button id="fsButton"><i class="fas fa-expand"></i></button>
        </div>

        <!-- The welcoming page -->
        <div id="welcome-page">
            <div class="welcome-container">
                <h1 class='welcome-title'><i>and we continue</i></h1>
                <div class="quote">
                    <q>Enlightenment is when the wave recognizes it is the ocean</q>
                    <p><i>- Thich Nhat Hanh</i></p>
                </div>
                <br>
                <p>
                    In this interactive presentation you will be able to explore the characteristics of water. 
                    While you start out as an individual, later you will be able to interact with other particpants by moving your avatar around. 
                    Together you will explore attraction, growth, chaos and ultimately 
                    <span class='equifinality' onmouseover="showPopup()" onmouseout="hidePopup()">equifinality
                        <span class="popup-equi" id="popupEqui">
                            Equifinality is the principle in open systems where a given end state can be reached by many potential means. 
                            <br>
                            It can also mean that a goal can be reached by many ways.
                        </span>
                    </span>.
                </p>
                <br>
                <h3>Instructions:</h3>
                <p><i class="fas fa-volume-up"></i> Make sure to turn up your volume!</i></p>
                <p><i class="fas fa-mouse-pointer"></i> When your screen is bright, click on empty space to guide your dot.</p>
                <p><i class="fas fa-mouse-pointer"></i> When the text 'Approach Others' appears, try coming together as a group.</p>
                <p><i class="fas fa-times-circle"></i> Or explore what happens if you don't follow these instructions! (please just don't turn off your sound!)</p>
                <br>
                <p>Make sure to use an up to date browser and large screen (laptop or desktop) to experience <i>and we continue</i>.</p>
                <button id="startButton">Enter the waiting room</button>

                <div class="extra-padding"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
    </div>
    <script src="featureCheck.js"></script>
    <script>
        // When the user clicks on <div>, open the popup
        function showPopup() {
          var popup = document.getElementById("popupEqui");
          popup.classList.add("show");
        }
        function hidePopup() {
          var popup = document.getElementById("popupEqui");
          popup.classList.remove("show");
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>